My, uh, my-my...

31:45.077 --> 31:47.949
my gut is telling me something,
and, um...

31:47.993 --> 31:49.429
- What?
- I-I think

31:49.472 --> 31:52.432
we should get Abby here.
You know?

31:52.475 --> 31:54.913
