my father of murder.

31:54.956 --> 31:57.524
- Are you hearing that?
- Yeah...

31:57.567 --> 31:59.830
Why would he murder
some random man?

31:59.874 --> 32:01.528
Ger, Ger,

32:01.571 --> 32:02.746
M-Mar...

32:02.790 --> 32:04.009
Marv, uh,

32:04.052 --> 32:06.925
w-wasn't random.

32:11.059 --> 32:12.843
Marv Davidson is, uh...

32:12.887 --> 32:13.888
What?

32:13.932 --> 32:15.672
...is your father.

32:15.716 --> 32:17.631
- What?!
- He's your birth father.

32:17.674 --> 32:19.067
No.

32:19.111 --> 32:20.634
Are you hearing yourself?

32:20.677 --> 32:22.853
Okay, listen...Are you hearing

32:22.897 --> 32:24.855
- what you're saying?
