32:24.899 --> 32:26.857
he-he... he went
to my mom, okay?

32:26.901 --> 32:29.164
And he told her...

32:29.208 --> 32:31.210
he had a child out there.

32:31.253 --> 32:32.515
- Stop.
- A child

32:32.559 --> 32:35.344
everyone thought was dead.

32:35.388 --> 32:38.434
But who wasn't dead.
Okay? Who-who...

32:39.435 --> 32:41.481
...who, uh, who isn't.

32:42.612 --> 32:45.354
Because I am...

32:45.398 --> 32:47.313
looking at her right now.

32:48.662 --> 32:51.708
I am not
Marv Davidson's daughter.

32:51.752 --> 32:53.972
Yeah.

32:54.015 --> 32:55.408
Pretty sure you are, Geri.

32:55.451 --> 32:58.193
Just as much
as you're Frank's.

32:58.237 --> 33:00.456
Hey.S... S...

33:00.500 --> 33:01.805
Just...

33:01.849 --> 33:03.982
I can't. I'm sorry, I c-I c...

33:04.025 --> 33:06.027
I cannot be here right now.

33:20.955 --> 33:24.480
Ger. Hey.

33:24.524 --> 33:26.004
Hey.

33:35.100 --> 33:37.754
Well... looks like

33:37.798 --> 33:40.018
you found your one good thing.

33:43.891 --> 33:45.632
Hey.
That man's testimony

33:45.675 --> 33:47.895
is gonna bring your daddy home.

33:47.938 --> 33:49.549
Not like this.

33:49.592 --> 33:52.073
Geri, I-I never wanted

33:52.117 --> 33:54.336
my-my one good thing to-to come

33:54.380 --> 33:56.425
at-at your expense.
Not like this.

33:57.426 --> 33:59.472
Doesn't change how it is.

34:00.864 --> 34:02.823
Hey, um...

34:04.129 --> 34:05.869
What Nate said--
it-it doesn't

34:05.913 --> 34:08.742
have to change
who your father was to you.

34:08.785 --> 34:10.657
He's still the man

34:10.700 --> 34:12.572
who raised you

34:12.615 --> 34:15.314
to be who you are today, okay?

34:15.357 --> 34:16.924
He's still your
port in the storm.

34:16.967 --> 34:18.447
- Yeah, I know.
- He...

34:19.883 --> 34:23.713
I-I know that you're trying
to help me right now, but...

34:23.757 --> 34:26.238
uh, may-maybe don't.

34:26.281 --> 34:28.022
Okay?

34:30.677 --> 34:33.897
Yeah.

34:33.941 --> 34:37.814
I have tried all day

34:37.858 --> 34:39.512
to help your family.

34:39.555 --> 34:43.255
I feel so stupid.

34:45.170 --> 34:46.780
Geri, my-my family

34:46.823 --> 34:49.739
is-is your family.

34:49.783 --> 34:51.698
We are family.

34:51.741 --> 34:54.135
You're-you're a Walker, still.

34:54.179 --> 34:56.311
Through and through.
This doesn't change anything.

34:56.355 --> 34:59.097
Cordi.

34:59.140 --> 35:01.055
Don't kid yourself.

35:01.099 --> 35:03.666
Did you-did you hear?

35:06.147 --> 35:08.454
