35:38.353 --> 35:39.876
I've never seen it empty.

35:41.400 --> 35:43.663
Yeah, me neither.

35:43.706 --> 35:45.839
You know, I walked in,

35:45.882 --> 35:49.059
and the first thing
that came to mind was

35:49.103 --> 35:51.149
that time that Liam

35:51.192 --> 35:53.934
covered that entire
wall with crayon.

35:55.544 --> 35:57.503
We told him he couldn't
play with them at the diner,

35:57.546 --> 36:00.158
and we said,
"Oh, use them at home."

36:00.201 --> 36:02.464
I didn't realize that
we'd have to specify,

36:02.508 --> 36:04.466
you know, that
the walls were off-limits.

36:04.510 --> 36:07.426
Yeah. Weird. I know...
I don't know

36:07.469 --> 36:09.732
- why I thought of that.
- Saying goodbye.

36:09.776 --> 36:12.126
You prepare for
the big memories. It's...

36:12.170 --> 36:13.910
it's the little ones that

36:13.954 --> 36:16.174
- catch you off guard.
- Yeah.

36:19.264 --> 36:21.570
Have you heard from Geri?

36:21.614 --> 36:23.659
No. I mean, I-I, um,

36:23.703 --> 36:25.618
I left some voice mails,

36:25.661 --> 36:27.576
but, uh...

36:27.620 --> 36:29.665
no, I haven't-haven't
heard back.

36:32.015 --> 36:35.367
I just can't believe it's her.

36:35.410 --> 36:38.065
That it was Geri-- our Geri--

36:38.108 --> 36:41.547
and... I had no idea.

36:41.590 --> 36:44.071
Mama...

36:44.114 --> 36:46.726
she doesn't blame you.
You know that.

36:46.769 --> 36:48.728
Not yet.

36:50.643 --> 36:52.166
Do you regret it?

36:52.210 --> 36:54.821
It wasn't easy,
or-or fun. But...

36:54.864 --> 36:57.867
if somebody had to say it,
I guess I'm glad it was me.

36:58.868 --> 37:00.653
Mm-hmm.

37:00.696 --> 37:02.220
Maybe tonight
you'll finally sleep.

37:02.263 --> 37:04.744
Yeah. Me and Daddy.

37:06.136 --> 37:08.095
What's that? You find
something in the move?

37:09.096 --> 37:10.663
Yeah.

37:10.706 --> 37:13.796
Something that I...
I thought was lost.

37:14.797 --> 37:16.625
Okay. Okay.

37:16.669 --> 37:17.626
Well, I guess we
should probably be...

37:17.670 --> 37:19.715
Can you give me a sec?

37:19.759 --> 37:22.240
Course. Yeah. Course.

38:09.896 --> 38:11.289
Hey, Dad.

38:15.641 --> 38:17.077
One last trip to the ranch?

38:17.120 --> 38:19.079
No.

38:19.122 --> 38:21.342
Nah, I don't want
to remember it like that.

38:21.386 --> 38:23.475
A shell of itself.

38:24.519 --> 38:26.521
