I have in my head.

38:27.914 --> 38:30.917
Side Step it is, then.

38:30.960 --> 38:33.267
We can't check
in to that hotel until 4:00.

38:33.311 --> 38:35.269
Y'all couldn't
scrounge up a rental?

38:35.313 --> 38:38.228
We had a couple things
going on, Dad.

38:38.272 --> 38:40.666
I know.

38:40.709 --> 38:42.450
Thank you, son.

38:42.494 --> 38:44.452
For believing in me.

38:44.496 --> 38:46.367
Always.

39:00.163 --> 39:01.687
- Hey.
- There he is.

39:01.730 --> 39:03.515
- Hey!
- Daddy.

39:03.558 --> 39:05.299
Ah! Oh!

39:07.823 --> 39:09.172
- Hey, little girl.
- Hi, there.

39:09.216 --> 39:10.652
