welcome back,

39:10.696 --> 39:12.915
Daddy. Uh, y-you-you
know, such-such as it is.

39:14.177 --> 39:15.396
All of us
together anywhere

39:15.440 --> 39:16.745
- is just fine.
- Mm-hmm.

39:16.789 --> 39:18.704
- Amen.
- Okay, sure,

39:18.747 --> 39:20.706
but, like, seriously...

39:20.749 --> 39:22.316
what are we gonna do
for breakfast?

39:22.360 --> 39:23.970
Okay, okay.

