You're here.

40:06.708 --> 40:08.318
Yeah.

40:09.929 --> 40:11.844
Um, I'm gonnaOkay, yeah.

40:11.887 --> 40:12.845
let you...Okay.

40:17.676 --> 40:20.374
Um...

40:20.418 --> 40:22.637
I-I... I am here.

